flowchart LR
    user[Healthcare staff / user] -->|Upload scanned PDF| s3in[Amazon S3 input bucket]
    s3in -->|ObjectCreated event| s3event1[S3 event notification]
    s3event1 --> bdalambda[BDA Trigger Lambda]
    bdalambda -->|Start extraction job| bda[Amazon Bedrock Data Automation]
    bda -->|Structured clinical JSON| s3out[Amazon S3 output bucket]
    s3out -->|ObjectCreated event| s3event2[S3 output event notification]
    s3event2 --> fhirlambda[FHIR Processor Lambda]
    fhirlambda -->|Map extracted fields| fhir[FHIR R4 bundle / NDJSON]
    fhir -->|Import job| healthlake[AWS HealthLake]
    healthlake -->|FHIR R4 endpoints| api[FHIR API query layer]
    api --> apps[Clinical apps / analytics / search]

    cloudwatch[Amazon CloudWatch] -. logs and metrics .- bdalambda
    cloudwatch -. logs and metrics .- fhirlambda
    cloudwatch -. alarms .- healthlake
    cloudtrail[AWS CloudTrail] -. API audit events .- bda
    cloudtrail -. API audit events .- healthlake
    iam[IAM roles and policies] -. least privilege access .- bdalambda
    iam -. least privilege access .- fhirlambda
    iam -. service permissions .- healthlake
    kms[AWS KMS] -. encryption keys .- s3in
    kms -. encryption keys .- s3out
    kms -. encryption keys .- healthlake
